dct_title_s: The National Geographic Magazine map of Africa
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Shows railroads, steamship lines, caravan routes, cable lines, overland telegraph lines, principal products, gold, silver and diamond fields, and territories. Supplement to The National Geographic Magazine, March 1909. Copyright, 1909, by the J.N. Matthews Co., Buffalo, N.Y. Suppl. to The National Geographic Magazine, March 1909.
dct_publisher_sm: [Washington, D.C. : National Geographic Society], 1909 (Buffalo, N.Y. : The Matthews-Northrup Works)
